OL,3,CBurglar targeted elderly victims in
OL,4,CNottinghamshire towns
OL,6,FThis Nottinghamshire burglar preyed on
OL,7,Felderly victims, leaving an 84-year-
OL,8,Fold woman feeling "mentally and
OL,9,Fphysically shattered".
OL,11,FNottingham Crown Court heard how John
OL,12,FLaughton tried to fool one wheelchair-
OL,13,Fbound victim he was chasing a burglar.
OL,15,FOn that occasion, the 56-year-old, who
OL,16,Fhad stayed out of trouble for 30 years
OL,17,Fbefore reoffending, fled from the
OL,18,Faddress in Sutton-in-Ashfield, empty-
OL,19,Fhanded.
