OL,6,FProsecutor Denney Lau said: "In a
OL,7,Fstatement, her family said their
OL,8,Fmother now felt unsafe in her own home
OL,9,Fand suffered two falls while checking
OL,10,Fdoors and windows.
OL,12,FShe is now in hospital and probably
OL,13,Fincapable of living independently as a
OL,14,Fresult of the ordeal."
