OL,6,FAnd he stole cash and a bank card,
OL,7,Fwith which he later made #135 gains,
OL,8,Fafter getting in through an unlocked
OL,9,Fdoor while an 84-year-old man slept.
OL,11,FLuc Chignell, mitigating, said
OL,12,FLaughton, of Co-Operative Street,
OL,13,FSutton-in-Ashfield, only has two
OL,14,Fprevious convictions dating back to
OL,15,F1992 and "describes his own behaviour
OL,16,Fas despicable."
