OL,6,FHe overcame a "terrible childhood" and
OL,7,Fbeat a drug addiction 33 years ago to
OL,8,Fgain work and raise a family. But he
OL,9,Fbecame homeless and relapsed into drug
OL,10,Fabuse after his marriage ended.
OL,12,FThe defendant pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fcharges of burglary, attempted
OL,14,Fburglary, theft and fraud at previous
OL,15,Fhearings.
